CRYSTAL APPLIED said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 15.65% to NT$190,632,000 from NT$225,988,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            190,632          225,988    
YOY%             -15.65%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            867,271         1,492,504   
YOY%             -41.89% 
=================================================================
 